column24: 5 - I am a natural born leader. Everywhere I go, I end up as the leader. If you want things to be done right, you should just make me the boss immediately. I am also extremely modest.
column25: 5 - One who constantly intervenes, verifies, evaluates and corrects the work of subordinates. If employees do not know that an extremely demanding and meticulous boss is watching their every step, they tend to get lazy and sloppy.
column26: 5 - I strongly prefer working with men.
